===Noun===
'''ester'''  (''plural:'' '''[[esters]]''')
# {{chemistry}}: A [[compound]] most often formed by the [[condensation]] of an [[alcohol]] and an [[acid]], with [[elimination]] of [[water]].  It contains the [[functional group]] [[carbon]]-[[oxygen]] [[double bond]] joined via [[carbon]] to another [[oxygen]] [[atom]].

See entry in [[w:Ester|Wikipedia]] or details.

